            "heading": "What are Cherokee Achieve men's scrubs?",
            "content": "Cherokee Achieve men's scrubs are athletic scrubs and active workwear built for male nurses, LPNs, RNs, medical assistants, and other healthcare professionals who work long shifts in hospital and clinical settings. Achieve is built around one idea: scrubs that move with you, not against you. That means Comfort Pro™ — Cherokee's exclusive double-brushed performance knit — delivering the comfort of your favorite sweats with the durability your shift actually demands. The men's line covers a tuck-in chest pocket V-neck top, a 3-pocket relaxed V-neck top, pull-on jogger pants, straight leg pants, and a zip-up warm-up jacket. Clean lines, no-bulk construction, and a relaxed fit that stays sharp on the floor."
          }
        },
